{"tid":965687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【血汗錢】康宏：12月強積金人均蝕約7800元 2018全年蝕2.1萬","createTime":"2019-01-02T09:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T05:20:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ed53d068d9910b3017453f85aae10491a06276a0","tid":965687,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190102/s00010/893cdeeaadbd190065ad02c8a6987f76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190102%2Fs00010%2F893cdeeaadbd190065ad02c8a6987f76.jpg&h=728fc2c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n康宏公布，截至2018年12月24日，康宏MPF綜合指數按月跌4.1%，年初至今就累計跌10.66%。以積金局2017年12月公布，強積金計劃成員數目共427萬計，2018年以來每成員平均蝕約21932元，12月單月計，人均蝕約7869元。<br />\n<br />\n康宏指出，由於市場預期美國加息步伐放緩，12月債券基金發揮避險作用，康宏MPF債券指數按月升1.24%，港元債券基金的表現最好，單月升1.25%，不過加息放緩就影響美股表現，12月最差的強積金類別為美國股票基金，單月份跌14.2%，2018年全年就跌12.38%。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，康宏各類基金中，只得3類2018年全年計可賺錢，分別是港元貨幣市場基金、強積金保守基金及港元債券基金，升幅為0.84%、0.59%及0.14%，其他23類基金均要蝕錢。2018年跌幅最大的三類基金分別是日本股票基金、亞洲(日本除外)股票基金及亞洲(日本及香港除外)股票基金，分別跌18.23%、17.82%及16.79%。<br />\n<br />\n以12月計，康宏旗下的港元債券基金、環球債券基金及人民幣債券基金就表現最佳，分別升1.25%、1.11%及0.75%。美國股票基金、環球股票基金及日本股票基金就表現最差，分別跌14.2%、10.98%及9.45%。<br />\n<br />\n康宏MPF指數以最少100隻規模最大的基金組成，覆蓋強積金市場總資產規模最少八成，並使用組合加權平均回報方法計算而成。<br />\n<br />\n記者：蕭嘉聰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1546415790363&amp;issue=20190102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1546415790363%26issue%3D20190102&d=Yp04jD2knAERE9relhoPIRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=021f043f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1546415790363%26issue%3D20190102&h=2c627dde\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1546415790363&amp;issue=20190102</a>"},{"pid":"552ee09bb56f28922b65ff026bd10d92091452b8","tid":965687,"uid":113178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"派$4000 都kum 唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c257f82e1b860e00eac17778c01de012255ecc","tid":965687,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1b3dea08e7c4dc82aaf805aca1ee76a7dd9438","tid":965687,"uid":29702,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ae2a175bff6b7b3b30896d10411e4429b16a625","tid":965687,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:22:49.000Z","msg":"攢粒糖，輸間廠"},{"pid":"414444e26454029bb59bea91c03e4cc741630b6e","tid":965687,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"12月轉走哂l"},{"pid":"69a7f4e34803c820551ea4aa40689a375957dba4","tid":965687,"uid":8219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"焗賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0706e9390d54697b0180b15568115c3c13d5e1a","tid":965687,"uid":27664,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:38:52.000Z","msg":"垃圾MPF，升嗰一兩千就聲大大，又sms又寄信通知你，跌四五千就影都唔見吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137424222c33c13130d81ce94b9f9e2c02f1c78a","tid":965687,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"咬老綜將會為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4708a602bee6053c93bd612c90c98c9359d68301","tid":965687,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"蝕到都唔撚想睇"},{"pid":"faa55622bcec494d357aac06b65a95bf56939bd4","tid":965687,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike